Package Description
insa.h4401.controller
Provides the classes necessary to control all elements of this applications.
insa.h4401.controller.command
Provides the classes necessary to manage all command of this applications.
insa.h4401.controller.states
Provides the classes necessary to navigate in the state machine of this application.
insa.h4401.delivery
This package is the application entry point The main method is in the MainApp class
insa.h4401.model
Provides the classes necessary to create the model for this application.
insa.h4401.utils
Provides the classes necessary to use generic tools The tools inside the Utils package can be used by all others classes of the projects.
insa.h4401.view
Provides the classes necessary to create the view for this application.
